${$json.chapterLengthMode === 'fixed' ? '- Approximately 2000-3000 words' : '- Write as much as this chapter needs to adequately develop its characters, advance its plot points, establish its settings, and resolve or set up its conflicts. Do not pad or rush — let the story dictate the length.'}

Begin the chapter now:` }] }) }}

